body:
@ the movie theater today they showed the trailer to Detective Pikachu (which I hadn’t watched until that moment) and like I knew Ryan Reynolds was voicing him but I thought they’d at least try???? Like that was deadass Ryan Reynolds. I thought they’d have made the voice higher or SOMETHING but NOOOOOO every person in the goddamn theater needs to know that its Ryan Reynolds

Detective Pikachu sounds more like Ryan Reynolds than Ryan fucking Reynolds
